      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "m_{u,s}(t) = σ(MLP(e_u ∥ e_s ∥ δ_{u,s}))  [Eq.12]\nP(u,q,t)   = σ(MLP(e_u ∥ e_q ∥ h_u(t) ∥ δ̄_q))  [Eq.13]\ndecay δ_{u,s} ∈ [0,1] — 4-stage cascade (Eq.6–11)\nper-skill P(mastery) and P(correct) for all enrolled skills",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
