      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  h_s  =  exp( 1.1  +  3.0·m_s  −  0.8·d_s )              ← calibrated half-life in days\n      m=0.0 → h≈ 2d  |  m=0.3 → h≈ 5d  |  m=0.6 → h≈12d  |  m=0.9 → h≈30d\n\n  retention(s)  =  2^( −1 / h_eff )                         h_eff = h_s × c     (c = consolidation bonus if practiced, else c = 1)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  h_s  =  exp( 1.1  +  3.0·m_s  −  0.8·d_s )              ← calibrated half-life in days\n      m=0.0 → h≈ 2d  |  m=0.3 → h≈ 5d  |  m=0.6 → h≈12d  |  m=0.9 → h≈30d\n\n  retention(s)  =  2^( −1 / h_eff )                         h_eff = h_s × c     (c = consolidation bonus if practiced, else c = 1)",
      "lineHeight": 1.3
    },
