      "text": "  Step 1 — HLR Forgetting  (every skill each day):\n      m_s  ←  floor_s  +  ( m_s − floor_s ) × 2^( −1/h_eff )\n\n  Step 2 — BKT Learning Gain  (practiced skills only):\n      p_success  =  σ( κ × ( m_s − θ ) )            [κ=steepness, θ=difficulty threshold]\n      zpd_weight =  max( 0.15,  1 − |m_s − z_c| / z_w )    [ZPD window around center z_c]\n      spacing_mult = 1 + 0.14 × min(gap−1, 7)              [spaced mode: testing-effect bonus]\n      Δm_s  =  η × zpd_weight × (1 − m_s) × p_success × spacing_mult\n      m_s   ←  min( 1.0,  m_s + Δm_s )",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  Step 1 — HLR Forgetting  (every skill each day):\n      m_s  ←  floor_s  +  ( m_s − floor_s ) × 2^( −1/h_eff )\n\n  Step 2 — BKT Learning Gain  (practiced skills only):\n      p_success  =  σ( κ × ( m_s − θ ) )            [κ=steepness, θ=difficulty threshold]\n      zpd_weight =  max( 0.15,  1 − |m_s − z_c| / z_w )    [ZPD window around center z_c]\n      spacing_mult = 1 + 0.14 × min(gap−1, 7)              [spaced mode: testing-effect bonus]\n      Δm_s  =  η × zpd_weight × (1 − m_s) × p_success × spacing_mult\n      m_s   ←  min( 1.0,  m_s + Δm_s )",
      "lineHeight": 1.3
    },
